author: Boston Dynamics
description:
The latest release of Spot & Orbit allows users to unlocks insights from maintenance and beyond, helping you understand the full health of your operations. It also includes the capabilities you need for enterprise-grade scale, so you can deploy and manage your fleet across multiple sites with less friction than ever.

Read more in our announcement: https://bostondynamics.com/blog/see-your-facility/

Sign-up for our webinar to learn about all the latest in 5.0: https://bostondynamics.com/webinars/plant-of-the-future-unlocking-full-facility-insights-with-ai/
title: New in Spot & Orbit 5.0 | Boston Dynamics
